{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend fuzz_json_io corpus with 5 orient + edge-case seeds\n\nThe fuzz_json_io corpus had 3 seeds (records, split, jsonl). Add 5\nmore covering the remaining JSON orients pandas supports, plus\nboundary cases:\n\n- columns_orient_seed: {col: {idx: val}} layout\n- index_orient_seed: {idx: {col: val}} layout\n- empty_records_seed: bare empty array []\n- single_record_seed: 1-row records with mixed scalar dtypes\n- jsonl_with_nulls_seed: JSON-lines with explicit null values\n\nEach seed exercises fuzz_json_io_bytes, which tries every JsonOrient\nplus jsonl until at least one parser succeeds, then asserts\nround-trip stability for the successful path.\n\n[bd-frankenpandas-shbif]\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
